# Netflix Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)

## Project Overview
This project analyzes Netflix movies and TV shows dataset using Python.

## Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Matplotlib
- Seaborn
- Jupyter Notebook

## Features
- Data Cleaning
- Missing Value Handling
- Data Visualization
- Trend Analysis

## Dataset
Netflix Movies and TV Shows Dataset

